142Status Callback::Skip(Reader* reader, std::uint64_t* bytes_remaining) {
143 assert(reader != nullptr);
144 assert(bytes_remaining != nullptr);
145
146 if (*bytes_remaining == 0)
147 return Status(Status::kOkCompleted);
148
149 Status status;
150 do {
151 std::uint64_t num_actually_skipped;
152 status = reader->Skip(*bytes_remaining, &num_actually_skipped);
153 *bytes_remaining -= num_actually_skipped;
154 } while (status.code == Status::kOkPartial);
155
156 return status;
157}
